OL,3,CCall for renters in Wales to get
OL,4,Ccompensation for no-fault eviction
OL,6,F"It was hard getting somewhere else
OL,7,Ffrom there, plus the cost of it all. I
OL,8,Fwas looking at needing a minimum of
OL,9,F#2,500 to get another property,"
OL,10,FJeffrey said, saying this would
OL,11,Finclude moving costs and the provision
OL,12,Fof one month's rent in advance.
OL,14,F"I'm a proud man. I was brought up
OL,15,F(to) fight, work, find a solution,
OL,16,Fthat there's always a light at the end
OL,17,Fof the tunnel. It was hard. I couldn't
OL,18,Fsee a light. Brick walls seemed to be
OL,19,Feverywhere," he said of the experience.
