OL,6,FHe added that, during the process, his
OL,7,Fchildren were concerned about where
OL,8,Fthey would end up going to school.
OL,10,F"It's a long process, it's a shame
OL,11,Fthey got wrapped up in it all," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
