OL,3,CCall for renters in Wales to get
OL,4,Ccompensation for no-fault eviction
OL,6,FThe Committee told the Welsh
OL,7,FGovernment that by April 2025 they
OL,8,Fshould publish their reasoning on
OL,9,Fwhether two-month rent compensation
OL,10,Ffor those facing eviction is feasible.
OL,12,FWith a law banning no-fault evictions
OL,13,Fcurrently making its way through the
OL,14,FHouse of Commons, the Committee says
OL,15,Fthe Welsh Government should monitor
OL,16,Fthe situation in England to ensure
OL,17,Fthat tenants in Wales don't end up
OL,18,Fworse off.
