OL,6,FThe report also found discrimination
OL,7,Fby landlords against people on
OL,8,Fbenefits as well as those with pets.
OL,10,FA 2022 survey by Shelter Cymru showed
OL,11,Fthat 37 per cent of landlords in Wales
OL,12,Fsay they do not, or prefer not, to let
OL,13,Fto tenants on benefits.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
