OL,3,CCall for renters in Wales to get
OL,4,Ccompensation for no-fault eviction
OL,6,FSome landlords also ask for several
OL,7,Fmonths' worth of rent in advance,
OL,8,Fwhich can make it difficult for people
OL,9,Fon low incomes to afford to rent. The
OL,10,Fcommittee has called on the Welsh
OL,11,FGovernment to regulate the sector and
OL,12,Fremove these types of financial
OL,13,Fbarriers.
OL,15,FIt is also calling for the Welsh
OL,16,FGovernment to explain how they intend
OL,17,Fto make pet ownership in rented
OL,18,Faccommodation a right, and to also
OL,19,Flaunch a campaign with landlords to
OL,20,Feliminate discrimination against pet
OL,21,Fowners.
