OL,4,Ccompensation for no-fault eviction
OL,6,FJeffrey, a dog-owner and part time
OL,7,Fworker, said he also encountered
OL,8,Fdifficulties finding somewhere to
OL,9,Frent, being asked about pets,
OL,10,Freceiving benefits, and whether or not
OL,11,Fhe smoked.
OL,13,F"Some (letting agencies) reduced the
OL,14,Fproperties I could apply for because I
OL,15,Fwas allowed it on benefits. Benefits
OL,16,Fprobably make up two thirds of my
OL,17,Fincome as a part time worker," he said.
OL,19,FHe says he doesn't want other people
OL,20,Fto go through the same experience as
OL,21,Fhim.
