OL,6,F"If it hadn't been for my kids, my
OL,7,Fgrandkids and my grandchildren, I
OL,8,Fmight have done something silly. It
OL,9,Fwas that bad, it literally broke me as
OL,10,Fa person," Jeffrey said.
OL,12,FJohn Griffiths MS, the Chair of the
OL,13,FLocal Government and Housing
OL,14,FCommittee, said: "Having a safe place
OL,15,Fto call home is a fundamental part of
OL,16,Fpeople being able to live happy,
OL,17,Fhealthy and fulfilling lives,
OL,18,Fregardless of whether that home is
OL,19,Fowned or rented.
OL,26,@vD@ROU
