OL,3,CCall for renters in Wales to get
OL,4,Ccompensation for no-fault eviction
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, this Committee heard
OL,7,Ffar too much evidence of people unable
OL,8,Fto find a stable home because they
OL,9,Fwere on benefits, couldn't afford huge
OL,10,Fup front deposits or had a pet. This
OL,11,Fdiscrimination, and the many other
OL,12,Fbarriers in people's way, must be
OL,13,Faddressed as soon as possible.
OL,15,F"And despite rules making no-fault
OL,16,Fevictions harder than they used to be,
OL,17,Fwe know that many people are still
OL,18,Fliving with the possibility of
OL,19,Feviction hanging over their heads.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
