OL,3,CCall for renters in Wales to get
OL,4,Ccompensation for no-fault eviction
OL,6,F"The private rented sector has to work
OL,7,Ffor both tenants and landlords. This
OL,8,Fis why we're urging the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment to implement our
OL,10,Frecommendations so that high-quality,
OL,11,Faffordable homes are available to all."
OL,13,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"Ensuring everyone in Wales has a
OL,15,Fdecent, affordable and safe place to
OL,16,Fcall home is one of our key ambitions
OL,17,Fand we will be publishing our White
OL,18,FPaper on Adequate Housing, Fair Rents
OL,19,Fand Affordability this month.
